{"type":null,"faqId":24791,"title":"荣耀 X2如何安装 SIM 卡和 microSD 卡？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:justify;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p5{text-indent:-0.19722222in;margin-left:1.6381944in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.045138888in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>安装 SIM 卡和 microSD 卡步骤如下：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.12.2.2.2.1.1\"></a><span>请使用随产品配送的专用顶针分别插入Micro SIM 卡座和 microSD/Nano SIM 卡座旁的小孔中，使卡座松开。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.12.2.2.2.2.1\"></a><span>轻轻取出卡座。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.12.2.2.2.3.1\"></a><span>按照图示方向将Micro SIM 卡和 microSD/Nano SIM 卡安装到卡座，并将卡座推回原位。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"figd0e3200\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=86219\" style=\"width:3.2291667in;height:3.1472223in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<a name=\"gen-id1.12.2.2.4\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=86220\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.12.2.2.4.1.1.1\"></a><span>上卡槽支持 Nano SIM 或 microSD 卡。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.12.2.2.4.1.2.1\"></a><span>下卡槽仅支持 Micro SIM卡，标准 SIM 卡的尺寸为：15 mm x 12 mm x 0.76 mm。请勿插入其他尺寸的 SIM 卡，以免损坏您的手机。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":176,"faqType":"其他","useful":1,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8791","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1430104345000,"seriesProductName":"GEM-703L","visitedTimes":448,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":9,"times":3,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"安装,卡,SIM卡,SD卡,插入","avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}